ow the game continued.} Bd7 {The move played by Caruana. Black's idea is to continue with f7-f5.} 18. Nh3 f5 {20.f4! Rc8 20.g3 Nc4 21.Bxc4 Rxc4 22.fxe5 f4 23.Nxf4 +- White was completely winning in Giri-Caruana 2016. The engine shows +6.60 after each of White's first top four moves! Caruana managed to save this game, and it ended with a draw.}) *

